The patch files in this directory are designed to be applied on top of Nekbone v2.3.4.

Source code:
    https://asc.llnl.gov/CORAL-benchmarks/Science/nekbone-2.3.4.tar.gz

Installation:

1. Acquire the source:
    wget https://asc.llnl.gov/CORAL-benchmarks/Science/nekbone-2.3.4.tar.gz

2. Unpack the source:
    tar zxvf nekbone-2.3.4.tar.gz

3. Change directories to the unpacked files.
    cd nekbone-2.3.4

4. Patch nekbone with the patch utility:
    patch -p1 < ../0001-Optimized-nekbone-code-for-Intel-hardware.patch
    patch -p1 < ../0002-Marked-up-nekbone-code-for-use-with-GEOPM.patch

5. Profit.
